---
title: Spiced Chicken & Rainbow Veggie Fries with Rocket-Pear Salad & Chive Aioli
description: Enjoy this bright and tasty dinner that gets a boost of flavour with our Nan's special seasoning! Serve up a side of
veggie fries and crunchy pear salad for a low-carb, but perfectly satisfying meal.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
